---
title: Hoisin & Ginger-Baked Salmon with Butter Rice & Creamy Slaw Shortcut ingredients | <5 min prep | Quick assembly
description: Enjoy a home-cooked meal with minimal prep and fuss! Simply pop the pre-prepped ingredients in the oven to cook and quickly assemble for a delicious and wholesome dinner. Let those pops of ginger in the hoisin sauce combine with the freshness of blushing salmon. You won’t be disappointed.
